snippet.title: Five Nights At Sonic's 3 - Reburned Teaser
snippet.description:
This video is about my upcoming game Five Nights At Sonic's 3 - Reburned.

This video showcases all max mode, and some new characters.

{There are some bugs and glitches still left in the game, and everything here could possibly change!}

(Sorry the video isnt the best quality, A higher quality causes lag!)
